c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. GrowthBar SEO is best suited for bloggers, solo marketers, small teams, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Surfer SEO, meanwhile, shines for content writers, SEO specialists, agencies, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2020, GrowthBar SEO describes itself as \"AI-powered SEO content writing tool with keyword research and optimization.\" Surfer SEO, established in 2017, positions itself as \"AI-powered content optimization tool for data-driven on-page SEO.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Surfer SEO** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (8.0 vs 6.0), more features (8 vs 6). However, this does not mean GrowthBar SEO is a poor choice — far from it. GrowthBar SEO excels in its own right, particularly for bloggers and solo marketers.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value best-in-class content optimization scoring, go with Surfer SEO. If good ai writing for blog content matters more to you, GrowthBar SEO is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
